1️⃣  Activate the virtual environment
=> source .venv/bin/activate

2️⃣ You’ll know it worked when your prompt shows:
=> (.venv) alexbrito@Alexs-MacBook-Pro ...

3️⃣ Install your package
=> pip install [package_name]

4️⃣ Run your Python scripts inside the virtual environment

cd path/to/your/project
source .venv/bin/activate